 points="4 0 36 20 4 40 4 0"></polygon></svg></div></div></button></div></li><li class="sc-lcIPJg inzaBa listItem    "><div class="sc-tagGq lakcSQ VideoListTextsContainer "><span class="sc-kdBSHD bIwAbd VideoListCount extraAlignmentMargin">1<!-- --> video</span><h3 class="sc-dCFHLb gvhOgC VideoListTitle "><span>Finding a Balance:</span></h3></div><div class="sc-esYiGF coZsKi VideoListThumbnailContainer"><button data-video-id="657781231.5d53b2b1da" class="sc-fjvvzt keAAAN VideoListThumbnail  " aria-label="play video: D. E. Shaw employee."><div class="sc-JrDLc bgaREO thumbnailWrapper"><div class="sc-hCPjZK gAaMvB border "></div><img alt="D. E. Shaw employee." src="/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657781231.5d53b2b1da.jpg" class="sc-fXSgeo lgwBdZ thumbnail"/><div class="sc-Nxspf gyQLGP playButton"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 40 40" style="margin-left:-2px"><polygon points="4 0 36 20 4 40 4 0"></polygon></svg></div></div></button></div></li><li class="sc-lcIPJg inzaBa listItem    "><div class="sc-tagGq lakcSQ VideoListTextsContainer "><span class="sc-kdBSHD bIwAbd VideoListCount ">3<!-- --> video<!-- -->s</span><h3 class="sc-dCFHLb gvhOgC VideoListTitle "><span>Internship Program:</span></h3></div><div class="sc-esYiGF coZsKi VideoListThumbnailContainer"><button data-video-id="1130345265" class="sc-fjvvzt keAAAN VideoListThumbnail  " aria-label="play video: D. E. Shaw employees collaborating in the office."><div class="sc-JrDLc bgaREO thumbnailWrapper"><div class="sc-hCPjZK gAaMvB border "></div><img alt="D. E. Shaw employees collaborating in the office." src="/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-1130345265.jpg" class="sc-fXSgeo lgwBdZ thumbnail"/><div class="sc-Nxspf gyQLGP playButton"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 40 40" style="margin-left:-2px"><polygon points="4 0 36 20 4 40 4 0"></polygon></svg></div></div></button><button data-video-id="1051852963" class="sc-fjvvzt keAAAN VideoListThumbnail  " aria-label="play video: D. E. Shaw employee."><div class="sc-JrDLc bgaREO thumbnailWrapper"><div class="sc-hCPjZK gAaMvB border "></div><img alt="D. E. Shaw employee." src="/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-1051852963.jpg" class="sc-fXSgeo lgwBdZ thumbnail"/><div class="sc-Nxspf gyQLGP playButton"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 40 40" style="margin-left:-2px"><polygon points="4 0 36 20 4 40 4 0"></polygon></svg></div></div></button><button data-video-id="858531388" class="sc-fjvvzt keAAAN VideoListThumbnail  " aria-label="play video: D. E. Shaw employees holding a clapperboard during a video production shoot."><div class="sc-JrDLc bgaREO thumbnailWrapper"><div class="sc-hCPjZK gAaMvB border "></div><img alt="D. E. Shaw employees holding a clapperboard during a video production shoot." src="/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-858531388.jpg" class="sc-fXSgeo lgwBdZ thumbnail"/><div class="sc-Nxspf gyQLGP playButton"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 40 40" style="margin-left:-2px"><polygon points="4 0 36 20 4 40 4 0"></polygon></svg></div></div></button></div></li></ul></div></section></div><div class="sc-jlZhew hPdEOb  "><section class="sc-cwHptR eRaOM  spaceBottom1 "><div class="WhoWeAre_hearFromTheGroupCallOutBoxContainer__9NhYo hearFromTheGroupCallOutBoxContainer"><div><aside class="sc-eqUAAy dNXyZV secondary1 WhoWeAre_hearFromOurPeopleCallOutBox__QyRVj"><section style="border:none" class="sc-fqkvVR cQWDvZ calloutBoxContainer"><a href="/careers/choose-your-path" target="_blank" class="sc-iGgWBj cjoYRU ArrowLongParent fontSerif" style="color:#FFFFFF;background:#252525;font-size:1.03em;line-height:1.44444;display:block"><div class="sc-dcJsrY jyZlaz mainSitePadding"><div><div class="cardIcon-module_CardIcon__fVUJp" style="display:inline-block;height:24px;width:24px"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="display:inline-block" fill="#252525"><path d="M16 18.28v-1.84A6 6 0 0 0 18 12V8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8v4a6 6 0 0 0 2 4.44v1.84L3 20v2l7-2.28v-2.08a5.89 5.89 0 0 0 4 0v2.08L21 22v-2zM8 12V8a4 4 0 0 1 8 0v4a4 4 0 0 1-8 0z"></path></svg></div><p class="sc-kAyceB eXbFpk PageTextBlockParagraph  wrapperClass   fontSerif " style="font-size:inherit;line-height:1.44444">Leave your suit at home, or wear one every day. No matter your wardrobe, our goal is to foster a supportive, flexible environment where you can do your best work.</p><div style="margin-top:1rem;display:unset"><div class="arrow-module_ArrowLong__sZPXB" id="ArrowLong" style="height:22px;width:28px;top:4px;position:relative"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 69 35.54" fill="#252525" style="top:4px"><g data-name="Layer 2"><g data-name="Layer 1"><g><polygon points="69 17.77 50.84 35.54 48.01 32.71 61.24 19.77 63.28 17.77 61.24 15.77 48.01 2.83 50.84 0 69 17.77"></polygon><rect y="15.77" width="66" height="4"></rect></g></g></g></svg></div><p class="sc-kAyceB eXbFpk PageTextBlockParagraph  wrapperClass   fontSerif " style="display:inline;padding-left:4px;position:relative;font-size:inherit;line-height:1.44444"><a href="/careers/choose-your-path" color="secondary1" style="display:inline-block;text-underline-offset:0.4em" target="_blank" class="sc-gEvEer dNokUJ  secondary1 Always fontSerif Varysize" tabindex="-1">Work at the D. E. Shaw group</a></p></div></div></div></a></section></aside></div></div></section></div></div><div class="sc-jlZhew hPdEOb  "><div class="sc-kMkxaj fkGzBE"><footer class="Footer "><div class="footerContent      "><div class="terms"><div class="termLinks"><div class="termLinksLeft"><p style="margin-bottom:6px"><a href="/assets/important-disclosure/Terms_and_Conditions_of_Use.pdf" color="secondary2" style="display:inline-block" target="_blank" class="sc-gEvEer jSFhCy  secondary2 Animated  Varysize" tabindex="0">Terms of Use</a></p><p style="margin-bottom:6px"><a href="/assets/important-disclosure/Privacy_Statement.pdf" color="secondary2" style="display:inline-block" target="_blank" class="sc-gEvEer jSFhCy  secondary2 Animated  Varysize" tabindex="0">Online Privacy Statement</a></p></div><div class="termLinksRight"><p style="margin-bottom:6px"><a href="/important-disclosures" color="secondary2" style="display:inline-block" class="sc-gEvEer jSFhCy  secondary2 Animated  Varysize" tabindex="0">Important Disclosures</a></p><p style="margin-bottom:6px"><a href="https://www.deshaw.com/impersonation-notice" color="secondary2" style="display:inline-block" target="_blank" class="sc-gEvEer jSFhCy  secondary2 Animated  Varysize" tabindex="0">Impersonation Notice</a></p></div></div><p>COPYRIGHT © 2018-2026 D. E. SHAW &amp; CO., L.P. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED</p></div><div class="info"><div class="social-media"><div class="icon-container"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/d.-e.-shaw-&amp;-co./" target="_blank" class="icon" rel="noreferrer"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 63 63"><g id="a"></g><g id="b"><g id="c"><path d="M63,4.542V58.458c0,2.503-2.025,4.542-4.5,4.542H4.485c-2.475,0-4.485-2.039-4.485-4.542V4.542C0,2.039,2.011,0,4.485,0H58.5c2.475,0,4.5,2.039,4.5,4.542ZM19.786,14.414c0-2.981-2.434-5.414-5.414-5.414-2.996,0-5.414,2.433-5.414,5.414s2.418,5.414,5.414,5.414,5.414-2.419,5.414-5.414Zm-.731,39.586V23.935H9.703v30.065h9.352Zm34.987-16.481c0-8.1-1.758-14.329-11.208-14.329-4.542,0-7.594,2.488-8.845,4.852h-.127v-4.106h-8.958v30.065h9.338v-14.878c0-3.924,.745-7.721,5.611-7.721,4.781,0,4.852,4.486,4.852,7.974v14.625h9.337v-16.481Z"></path></g></g></svg></a><a href="http://www.youtube.com/@deshawgroup" target="_blank" class="icon" rel="noreferrer"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 56.667 68"><g id="a"></g><g id="b"><g id="c"><path d="M7.514,0h4.08l2.799,10.489L16.989,0h4.12l-4.718,15.598v10.645h-4.055V15.598L7.514,0ZM26.197,6.724c-3.171,0-5.273,2.097-5.273,5.199v9.489c0,3.411,1.782,5.188,5.273,5.188,2.896,0,5.174-1.935,5.174-5.188V11.923c0-3.029-2.258-5.199-5.174-5.199Zm1.505,14.527c0,1.054-.538,1.83-1.507,1.83-.995,0-1.57-.813-1.57-1.83V12.243c0