5.836-1.195-8.831-1.195s-6.019,.408-8.831,1.195c0,0-6.765-4.711-9.703-3.797-1.927,4.866-.731,8.635-.366,9.549-2.25,2.475-3.318,4.416-3.318,8.283,0,13.527,7.932,14.667,15.792,15.539-1.012,.928-1.926,2.488-2.25,4.738-2.011,.929-7.172,2.489-10.251-2.938-1.927-3.347-5.429-3.628-5.429-3.628-3.445-.043-.225,2.165-.225,2.165,2.306,1.055,3.909,5.147,3.909,5.147,2.067,6.3,11.911,4.19,11.911,4.19,0,2.953,.042,7.763,.042,8.634,0,.914-.633,2.025-2.433,1.702C9.815,63.253,0,49.908,0,34.312,0,14.808,14.92,0,34.425,0s35.325,14.808,35.325,34.312Z"></path></g></g></svg></a></div></div><div class="headquarters"><p>New York City HQ</p><p>Two Manhattan West</p><p>375 Ninth Avenue</p><p>New York, NY 10001</p></div><div class="navigationWrapper navigation-wrapper "><ul class="subNavigation sub-navigation"><li class="main-title"> <a href="http://investors.deshaw.com/" color="secondary2" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:top" target="_blank" class="sc-gEvEer jSFhCy  secondary2 Animated  Varysize" tabindex="0">Investor Login</a></li></ul></div></div></div></footer></div></div></div></div><section class="sc-jXbUNg feXDOs" aria-label="Cookie Banner"><div class="sc-dhKdcB kuWXtn">By visiting our website, you agree to our<!-- --> <a rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.deshaw.com/assets/important-disclosure/Privacy_Statement.pdf" color="secondary1" target="_blank" class="sc-gEvEer dNokUJ  secondary1 Always  Varysize" tabindex="0">Online Privacy Statement</a> <!-- -->and our<!-- --> <a rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.deshaw.com/assets/important-disclosure/Terms_and_Conditions_of_Use.pdf" color="secondary1" target="_blank" class="sc-gEvEer dNokUJ  secondary1 Always  Varysize" tabindex="0">Terms of Use</a>, which include a class action waiver and an arbitration provision. Clicking “Accept All” means you consent to our use of cookies and similar tracking technologies, such as analytics cookies provided by third-party companies, which help us understand how our website is used. Clicking “Decline All” means you prevent us from using non-essential cookies or other similar tracking technologies on our website; however, we will continue to use essential cookies for the core functions of our website, including security.</div><div class="sc-kpDqfm jnDBBH"><button class="sc-dAlyuH bYmxqf">Accept All</button><button class="sc-dAlyuH eZEfGd">Decline All</button></div></section></div><script id="__NEXT_DATA__" type="application/json">{"props":{"pageProps":{"routes":{"home":"/","whoWeAre":"/who-we-are","whatWeDo":"/what-we-do","careers":"/careers","investorLogin":"/irweb","news":"/news","library":"/library","contact":"/contact","whoWeAreIntro":"/who-we-are","leadership":"/who-we-are/leadership","founder":"/who-we-are/founder","corePrinciples":"/who-we-are/core-principles","ourPeople":"/who-we-are/our-people","whatWeDoIntro":"/what-we-do","investmentManagement":"/what-we-do/investment-management","technology":"/what-we-do/technology-development","managingRisk":"/what-we-do/risk-management","entrepreneurship":"/what-we-do/entrepreneurship","industryLeadership":"/what-we-do/industry-leadership","careersIntro":"/careers","careerDevelopment":"/careers/career-development","chooseYourPath":"/careers/choose-your-path","interviewing":"/careers/interviewing","benefits":"/careers/benefits","internships":"/careers/internships"},"hearFromTheGroupVideos":[{"sectionTitle":"Making an Impact:","videos":[{"videoId":"657781712.69e1538d9e","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Nan, Quantitative Analyst:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657781712.69e1538d9e.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657781712.69e1538d9e.jpg","videoDescription":" “What I find the most exciting here is that I never get bored of my work. I always get very interesting problems I can keep working on.”"}]},{"sectionTitle":"Discovering the Firm:","videos":[{"videoId":"657780943.7722ff0ed6","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Jay, Counsel:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657780943.7722ff0ed6.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657780943.7722ff0ed6.jpg","videoDescription":" “In a thirty minute conversation, you wouldn’t think you’d get into that much detail, but we did.”"},{"videoId":"657781019.c15087b776","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Josh, Quantitative Analyst:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657781019.c15087b776.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657781019.c15087b776.jpg","videoDescription":" “I thought I’d try this out for a year, and fifteen years later I’m still sitting here.”"},{"videoId":"657781546.243fc2f41f","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Nan, Quantitative Analyst:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657781546.243fc2f41f.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657781546.243fc2f41f.jpg","videoDescription":" “I didn’t have a good sense of finance, so I was expecting to see people in suits.”"}]},{"sectionTitle":"Work \u0026 Process:","videos":[{"videoId":"657780793.1de91f79fa","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Greg, Trader:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657780793.1de91f79fa.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657780793.1de91f79fa.jpg","videoDescription":" “The way we approach problem solving makes it so much more research focused, you feel like you’re almost within an academic institution.”"},{"videoId":"657781310.6e57cd6aa8","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Marianna, Portfolio Manager:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657781310.6e57cd6aa8.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657781310.6e57cd6aa8.jpg","videoDescription":" “It’s really exciting to come and help build a business at an institution like this one. There’s so much support from all different parts of the firm.”"},{"videoId":"657783083.7c076d8143","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Zack, Investor Relations:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657783083.7c076d8143.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657783083.7c076d8143.jpg","videoDescription":" “What you know coming in is much less important than what you’re willing to learn once you get here.”"}]},{"sectionTitle":"Culture \u0026 Colleagues:","videos":[{"videoId":"657780741.98e16af892","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Greg, Trader:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657780741.98e16af892.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657780741.98e16af892.jpg","videoDescription":" “I found that the employees of the D. E. Shaw group are exceptionally well-rounded; that’s not an adjective I expected to use.”"},{"videoId":"657780853.7c78000b26","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Jay, Counsel:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657780853.7c78000b26.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657780853.7c78000b26.jpg","videoDescription":" “We’re comfortable in our nerdiness, and the firm kind of encourages it.”"},{"videoId":"657781458.df28b25090","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Nan, Quantitative Analyst:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657781458.df28b25090.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657781458.df28b25090.jpg","videoDescription":" “It’s sort of like a mixture of grad school and a tech company, with a flavor of finance in it.”"},{"videoId":"657782989.be80d16854","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Zack, Investor Relations:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657782989.be80d16854.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657782989.be80d16854.jpg","videoDescription":" “My fellow employees are relentlessly rational. At the end of the day, what matters most is that they get things right.”"}]},{"sectionTitle":"Finding a Balance:","videos":[{"videoId":"657781231.5d53b2b1da","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Meet Marianna, Portfolio Manager:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-657781231.5d53b2b1da.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-657781231.5d53b2b1da.jpg","videoDescription":" “I think working in this city is the best thing you can do for being in this industry and being a mom, because there’s a huge support network.”"}]},{"sectionTitle":"Internship Program:","videos":[{"videoId":"1130345265","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employees collaborating in the office.","videoHighlightText":"Hear our interns reflect on their memorable summer experience:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-1130345265.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-1130345265.webp","videoDescription":" “The pace of learning has been super fast, and that’s a part I enjoy a lot about being here.”"},{"videoId":"1051852963","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employee.","videoHighlightText":"Hear our interns reflect on their memorable summer experience:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-1051852963.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-2024-Intern-Scrapbook-2.webp","videoDescription":"“It’s not about how much you know going into the internship… it’s how much you develop.”"},{"videoId":"858531388","videoAltText":"D. E. Shaw employees holding a clapperboard during a video production shoot.","videoHighlightText":"Hear our interns reflect on their memorable summer experience:","iconSrc":"/img/video-images/icons/de-shaw-858531388.jpg","imgBackgroundSrc":"/img/video-images/background/de-shaw-2023-Intern-Scrapbook-1.webp","videoDescription":"“Everyone is so curious, thoughtful, and intellectual.”"}]}],"corePrinciples":[{"title":"Hire and Cultivate Extraordinary People","content":"The quality of our staff is largely responsible for the firm’s success and reputation, and is one of the main reasons that exceptional people are interested in working here. We don’t compromise when it comes to recruiting and developing world-class talent. We give special attention to candidates with extraordinary raw ability and long-term potential."},{"title":"Take the High Road","content":"We have an inviolable policy of maintaining the highest ethical and legal standards and treating colleagues with respect and professionalism.  This policy protects our reputation; more importantly, it’s simply the right thing to do. In conducting our business, we consider not only the letter, but also the spirit of the law."},{"title":"Set Unusually Ambitious Goals","content":"We were built in part by trying things that others either considered infeasible or simply never thought of. A single transformative idea that ultimately reaches fruition may be worth a hundred that wind up leading nowhere, and the risk of repeated failures may be justified by the value of a single major success. When an extraordinary team sets extraordinarily ambitious goals, \u0026#8220;unexpected\u0026#8221; breakthroughs are to be expected."},{"title":"Focus on the Firm as a Whole","content":"Our culture is based on a collaborative environment in which individuals and groups work together to advance their mutual interests and those of the firm. Employees and groups are valued for their collective contributions to our overall success."},{"title":"Analyze Rigorously and Communicate Clearly","content":"We place an extraordinarily high value on systematic analysis and precise communication. We take an unusually rigorous and disciplined approach to the processes of planning, evaluation, forecasting, and decision-making, and we believe this has contributed materially to our success over the years."}]},"__N_SSG":true},"page":"/who-we-are/[[...slug]]","query":{"slug":["core-principles"]},"buildId":"QiKE25N6-kjoBgGag7Qon","isFallback":false,"gsp":true,"locale":"en","locales":["en"],"defaultLocale":"en","scriptLoader":[]}</script></body></html>